</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_513" id="256r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_513_r1l2">Franckfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_513_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als die <expan>ſtallu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den Edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den von Hanaw </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l4">vnd vns <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> ın der meſſe auſʒgeet / <expan>Hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir dem vvılhelm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l5">Mendell <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l6">vveıſheit dauon cʒu reden als Er 
<del rend="strikethrough">d </del> ew das wol ercʒelen vvirdet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l7"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> // daʒ Jr <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Ratgeſellen darynne von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvegen fürderlich vnd geraten ſein wöllet / Als das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l9">vveiſheit vormals auch williklich getan hat / des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l10"><expan>erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> freuntſchaft mit gancʒem fleiſʒ dancken / vnd auch das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l11">in <expan>ſolch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſachen v̈mb ewr vveıſheit allcʒeit gern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_513_r1l12">verdienen <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egıdıȷ / Anno <expan>duodecı<ex>m</ex>o</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_513" id="256r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Franckfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als die <expan>stallu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        den von Hanaw und uns <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> in der messe
                        auszgeet, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir dem Wilhelm Mendell,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesellen,
                            <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        weisheit davon czu reden, als er ew das wol erczelen wirdet.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> ratgesellen darynne von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen fürderlich und geraten sein wöllet,
                        als das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> weisheit vormals auch williklich getan
                        hat; des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan> freuntschaft mit ganczem fleisz dancken und
                        auch das in <expan>solch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sachen ümb ewr weisheit allczeit gern
                        verdienen <expan>wolle<ex>n.</ex></expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii anno
                                <expan>duodeci<ex>m</ex>o</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
